## 实现步骤

基于查询结果和 SDK 事件维护你自己的集合状态。

```ts
const state = createMessageStore();

state.replacePage(
  await OpenIM.getAdvancedHistoryMessageList({
    conversationID,
    startClientMsgID: '',
    count: 30,
    viewType: 0,
  }),
);

OpenIM.on(CbEvents.OnRecvNewMessages, ({ data }) => {
  state.mergeIncoming(data);
});
```

