kickGroupMember: <T>(data: AccessToGroupParams, operationID?: string) => Promise<WsResponse<T>>;
changeGroupMemberMute: <T>(data: ChangeGroupMemberMuteParams, operationID?: string) =>
  Promise<WsResponse<T>>;
addBlack: <T>(data: AddBlackParams, operationID?: string) => Promise<WsResponse<T>>;
```

相关事件：

```ts
on<E extends CbEvents>(event: E, fn: Cbfn<E>): this;
off<E extends CbEvents>(event: E, fn: Cbfn<E>): this | undefined;
CbEvents.OnGroupMemberDeleted
CbEvents.OnBlackAdded
```

响应和事件载荷使用以下通用结构：

```ts
type WsResponse<T> = {
  event: string;
  errCode: number;
  errMsg: string;
  data: T;
  operationID: string;
};
type WSEvent<T = unknown> = {
  event: CbEvents;
  data: T;
  errCode: number;
  errMsg: string;
  operationID: string;
};
```

## 实现步骤

群组内管理使用 SDK 能力，账号级封禁放在后端实现。

```ts
await OpenIM.kickGroupMember({
  groupID,
  reason: 'Removed by moderator',
  userIDList: [targetUserID],
});

await backend.banUser({ targetUserID, reason });
```

